---
title: Pork Meatballs in Creamy Chive Sauce with Chips and Green Beans
description: These Pork Meatballs in Creamy Chive Sauce are a crowd pleaser and one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
